        "   v(0,t) &= 0 && 0 < t < \\infty \\\\ \n",
        "   v(1,t) &= \\color{red}{\\delta(t)} && \\\\\n",
        "   v(x,0) &= 0 && 0 \\leq x \\leq 1\n",
        "  \\end{aligned}$$ \n",
        "\n",
        "* Knowing this formula\n",
        "\n",
