        "Lets use substitution:\n",
        "Let $\\xi = \\frac{x - a}{b - a}$, so $x = (b-a)\\xi + a$, $dx = (b-a) d\\xi$, and when $x = a \\Rightarrow \\xi = 0, x = b \\Rightarrow \\xi = 1$\n",
        "\n",
        "Then:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$(x - a)(b - x) = (b - a)^2 \\xi (1 - \\xi)$$\n",
        "\n",
