        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Solution**\n",
        "\n",
        "**Step 1:** $~$ Separation of Variables\n",
        "\n",
        "Lets look for a solution of the form:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$u(x,t) = X(x)T(t)$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Plug into the PDE:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$X(x) T(t) = \\alpha X(x) T(t)\n",
