        "\n",
        "With Neumann boundary conditions:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$X'(0) = 0, \\quad X'(\\pi) = 0$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Step 2:** $~$ Solve the Spatial ODE\n",
        "\n",
        "$$X'' + \\lambda X = 0$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Solutions depend on the value of $\\lambda$:\t\n",
        "\n",
        "* The eigenfunctions satisfying Neumann BCs are:\n",
        "\n",
