        "**3.** $~$ Solve the problem\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{aligned}\n",
        " u_{t} &= u_{xx} +F(x,t), \\;\\; -\\infty < x < \\infty, \\;\\; t>0\\\\ \n",
